# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share this in the project to support other developers
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in git
#   However, in case of microservices or apps, you can keep Pipfile.lock in git.
#   Pipfile.lock is NOT ignored by default.

# poetry
#   Similarly, poetry.lock is NOT ignored.

# pdm
#   Similarly, pdm.lock is NOT ignored.

# uv
#   Similarly, uv.lock is NOT ignored.

